{"tid":1611454,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中槍中五生情況轉為穩定 另兩人危殆","createTime":"2019-10-02T03:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T04:47:35.000Z","uid":68738,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a6009edf16d42c2678082823ae2234893c89a9","tid":1611454,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:16:28.000Z","msg":"昨天「黑色十.一」，全港多區均有公民抗命集會或遊行抗爭，多人在衝突中受傷。今早醫管局提供最新數字顯示，共104人送院，除了中槍的中五生曾志健，情況由危殆轉為穩定外，目前仍有兩名傷者留醫情況危殆。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局稱，截至今早10時，全港12間公立醫院共接收104名傷者，分別是81男23女，年齡介乎11至75歲。現時兩名男子危殆，留醫東區醫院及律敦治醫院；兩名男子嚴重；29人情況穩定或滿意（當中一人為曾志健），71人經治理後出院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191002/60107233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60107233&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=6de22d5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60107233&h=e4c03bcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191002/60107233</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab59adbfa1ac16f8931917664f5a5c20c7aa7f73","tid":1611454,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:17:31.000Z","msg":"辛苦曬醫護人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e05c6c0f1919c4f9202789bdaae3f53845ed544","tid":1611454,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:18:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府即將告你暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有全民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無&middot;限&middot;期</span>罷工罷課先可以救自己、救義士！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，今日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協，答應五大訴求為止！</span>"},{"pid":"0b893677502f4c55b660318c7b375695e2e23f51","tid":1611454,"uid":74091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩冇生命危險"},{"pid":"ead2912757eec30b8373578d0c97eaaca78f57c1","tid":1611454,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571da1503af051d15bc0d3205e4e28ce497b8a44","tid":1611454,"uid":55956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:28:13.000Z","msg":"兩名男子危殆..即係中其他彈或者打到仆街"},{"pid":"f6c7ef865d1ea2fdc24cada99e9b407b9065cd1e","tid":1611454,"uid":173011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:33:05.000Z","msg":"有冇另外兩人嘅資料？<br />\n雖然冇中鎗，但唔好當佢哋係condom啊"},{"pid":"0a654e44ceb6f8736d569081e8d3c9795b88213c","tid":1611454,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:33:16.000Z","msg":"對準政權 全民公投實行雙普選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609445</a>"},{"pid":"cfe6a61b9629075df5904238d5f4cadee5bd227b","tid":1611454,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:33:23.000Z